title: Get clear on what you want.
message: If you don’t know exactly what you want, you can’t actually take steps to make it happen. To manifest something, you must know what you desire.

user.name: Marjatta
user.headline: Thanks for reaching out Mia. I will help you how to take Action to manifest what you want
